sentences: Roswell joined Spacemen 3 in 1987 as drummer, and performed on the albums The Perfect Prescription and Performance.
After leaving Spacemen 3, he joined The Darkside in 1989 – alongside Spacemen 3 bandmate Pete Bain – and recorded three albums with the band.
In 2004 he issued the solo album the Psychedelic Ubik under his own name on Mint/Jungle Records.
